item.title: Prayer bpn12987 in Kuanua
item.description: A iangim ia kaugu varvalagar, U kaugu Luluai, ma Kaum varvanuknuk ia ra gu varvalaun. Kimaravai piram ia kaugu gaga ma Kaum varmananai iana bona talaigu. Kaum varmari ia kaugu varvalaun ma a maravut ta gono ra gunagunan ma tara gunan namur bula. (Source category: A NIARING UPI RA VARVALAGAR) (Bahaiprayers.net ID: 12987)
